{"id":37497,"date":"2024-02-02T11:18:07","date_gmt":"2022-09-02T05:48:07","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=37497"},"modified":"2023-03-31T16:16:21","modified_gmt":"2023-03-31T10:46:21","slug":"decorative-wall-mirrors","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/decorative-wall-mirrors\/","title":{"rendered":"Decorative Wall Mirrors: Amazing Ideas To Make Your Home Decor A Work Of Art"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Get a taste of the finer things in life with these wall mirror decorating ideas you can try out on a budget.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Is understanding how decor works daunting to you? Are there times when you are stuck looking for the right decor piece for your home which ultimately leads you to give up on decorating your place? Are you always wondering what can go on this particular wall in my home? Well, this blog is going to solve all those problems for you at once. This blog is your guide to some of the finest decorative wall mirror ideas that may answer all your questions right away. So, without further ado, let\u2019s dive right into the topic and check out some inspiring wall mirrors that we are absolutely drooling over.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Decorating Your Foyer Area With A Collage Of Circle Mirrors<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>The foyer area in your home is often the most undervalued space. Many just use it to place their footwear, not knowing how to make it a decor success. And this is where our expertise enters! Decorating with circle mirrors can be a great addition to the foyer area in your home. Not only does it make the space look stylish, but it also creates an illusion of a larger space. In fact, decorating with circle mirrors allows you to accentuate the rest of your space easily. Striking a balance between both rounded elements like the mirror and sharp-edged ones like cabinets can help sweep in a sense of design and style at your home.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110544\/decorative-wall-mirrors-for-foyer-area.jpg\" alt=\"Decorative wall mirrors to decorating your foyer area\" class=\"wp-image-37501\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110544\/decorative-wall-mirrors-for-foyer-area.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110544\/decorative-wall-mirrors-for-foyer-area-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110544\/decorative-wall-mirrors-for-foyer-area-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110544\/decorative-wall-mirrors-for-foyer-area-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Accentuate the foyer with decorative wall mirrors<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Place A Decorative LED Mirror Near Your Home Entrance<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Backlit wall mirrors are a class apart. They are in line with the latest decor trends, elegant in look and are such a great decor option for your entryway. We love this decorative LED mirror for the entryway that has an LED backlight with a design that has multiple circle mirrors entwined together. What\u2019s great about these mirrors is that they feature soft lighting and can double as a wall soft light lamp as well for warm and cosy evenings.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110531\/decorative-led-mirror-for-entryway.jpg\" alt=\"Decorative LED mirror for your home entrance\" class=\"wp-image-37499\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110531\/decorative-led-mirror-for-entryway.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110531\/decorative-led-mirror-for-entryway-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110531\/decorative-led-mirror-for-entryway-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110531\/decorative-led-mirror-for-entryway-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Decorative LED mirror for a bright entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Go The Classic Route With A Rectangle Decorative Mirror<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Go the perennial route with something that coordinates with the rest of the design and patterns in the room. In this picture, you can see how the edged mirror simply blends into the setting and compliments the rest of the modular furnishings, right from the wall-mounted shelf and the tiled walls to the main entrance door.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110556\/rectangle-decorative-wall-mirrors.jpg\" alt=\"Rectangle decorative mirror for a classic entrance\" class=\"wp-image-37503\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110556\/rectangle-decorative-wall-mirrors.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110556\/rectangle-decorative-wall-mirrors-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110556\/rectangle-decorative-wall-mirrors-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110556\/rectangle-decorative-wall-mirrors-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A rectangle decorative mirror for a classic entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Keep It Simple With A Large Round Decorative Mirror<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you don\u2019t fancy too many mirrors clubbed together or the LED backlit ones, you can always choose to go the minimalist route. Decorating with circle mirrors is multi-functional. It\u2019s a class apart and can simply work with any part of your room. For instance, in the image below, the simple but classic large round decorative mirror does an outstanding job of making the area look attractive. It completes the visual play of this living space.&nbsp;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110602\/round-decorative-wall-mirrors.jpg\" alt=\"Decorative wall mirror with a large round decorative mirror for simple look\" class=\"wp-image-37504\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110602\/round-decorative-wall-mirrors.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110602\/round-decorative-wall-mirrors-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110602\/round-decorative-wall-mirrors-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110602\/round-decorative-wall-mirrors-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>A large round decorative mirror for visual aesthetics<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Mirror Art Wall Decor As A Centrepiece In The Living Room<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Mirrors aren\u2019t simply restricted to your bedroom or foyer\/entryway. You can choose to use them to your benefit in your living room as a wall centrepiece. However, when opting for a centrepiece for your living room, look out for modern decorative wall mirrors that come with some bling and some character. Adding character to your living space can greatly enhance the overall appearance of your home. In this image, you can find a large wall mirror with a sharp wooden palette that adds to the rustic bohemian vibe of the space.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110550\/mirror-wall-decor-for-living-room.jpg\" alt=\"Mirror art wall decor for living room adds to the rustic bohemian vibe\" class=\"wp-image-37502\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110550\/mirror-wall-decor-for-living-room.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110550\/mirror-wall-decor-for-living-room-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110550\/mirror-wall-decor-for-living-room-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/02110550\/mirror-wall-decor-for-living-room-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption>Centrepiece mirrors for a modern rustic flair<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Remember, when you have an empty wall and nothing strikes your mind, a head turner like a sun-inspired decorative wall mirror can be a fine choice. This can also easily replace your living room centrepiece or work great for your bedroom\u2019s accent wall. If not, you can always place them in the foyer area and call it a day!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"End-to-end home interior design solutions for a stunning home\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/08180939\/end-to-end-home-interior-design-solutions-for-stunning-home.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<p>Phew! That\u2019s a lot of mirror talk all in one blog, enticing enough? Now chance upon our highlight on how to spruce up dull walls using <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-decor\/wall-decor-painting-ideas\/\">DIY Wall Decor Painting Ideas<\/a> for your home.<\/p>\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Looking For Functional Interior Designs?<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with smart solutions<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_quote_action.php\" method=\"post\"\n    novalidate=\"novalidate\">\n    <div class=\"form-group\">\n        <input type=\"text\" class=\"form-control\"  name=\"your-name\" placeholder=\"Enter your name*\" \/>\n        <!-- <span class=\"sales-txt-label\" id=\"labeltxt\">Enter your name*<\/span>  -->\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"form-row dc-falg-row\">\n        <!-- <div class=\"form-group col-md-3 guideForm\">\n            <select name=\"your-phone-ext\" id=\"id_select2_example\" class=\"id_select2_example drop-downfield form-dropdown\"\n                onfocus='this.size=5;' onblur='this.size=1;' onchange='this.size=1; this.blur();'\n                data-width=\"100%\" data-minimum-results-for-search=\"Infinity\">\n               \n                <option value=\"+01\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06163948\/01.png\">\n                    +01\n                <\/option>\n                <option value=\"+91\"\n                    data-img_src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/10\/06164015\/91.png\"\n                    selected>\n                    +91\n                <\/option>\n           